ymore, you are now competing with Africa, and the competition is FIERCE!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Appear at the top when a hot lead is searching for products or services related to you<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get the hook right! &#8211; Messaging on your ads and social platforms is the key -Don&#8217;t worry we will do it for you<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be smart: &#8211; Only pay for your leads (When a lead clicks on your ad, stop paying for useless clicks)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It takes real strategy and insight to be effective. Paid digital ads sound simple: you buy ads and they appear, like a print product. It\u2019s not\u2014with paid digital ads, you \u2018bid\u2019 on keywords, and only pay when someone clicks on one. Because there are a lot of keywords, competition can be fierce. That\u2019s why PPC is a science and an art. You want to make sure that your best, most highly-targeted customers are clicking on your ad, and you don\u2019t want to pay for useless clicks.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Services Include: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ROI conversion tracking, Campaign, ad group, ad and bid management and optimisation, A\/B page layout testing, Landing page optimisation<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row row_type=&#8221;row&#8221; use_row_as_full_screen_section=&#8221;no&#8221; type=&#8221;grid&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;93&#8243; padding_bottom=&#8221;100&#8243; css_animation=&#8221;&#8221; box_shadow_on_row=&#8221;no&#8221; oblique_section=&#8221;no&#8221; triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;58236&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; qode_hover_animation=&#8221;&#82